### Cinema Pricing Service - HTTP Requests
### Use IntelliJ IDEA's HTTP Client to execute these requests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@apiPath = /api/v1/tickets/calculate-pricing

### Example 1: Senior with Children (Bulk Discount)
POST {{baseUrl}}{{apiPath}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": 1,
  "customers": [
    {
      "name": "John Smith",
      "age": 70
    },
    {
      "name": "Jane Doe",
      "age": 5
    },
    {
      "name": "Bob Doe",
      "age": 6
    }
  ]
}

